OL,3,CCharities fear 'shortsighted' funding
OL,4,Ccuts will put vulnerable people at risk
OL,6,FITV News' Richard Payne spoke to
OL,7,Fcharities about what these cuts could
OL,8,Fmean for them.
OL,10,FCharities supporting some of the most
OL,11,Fvulnerable people in Bath say they are
OL,12,Fworried about what future support they
OL,13,Fwill be able to provide following
OL,14,Fproposed cuts to the funding they
OL,15,Freceive.JBath & North East Somerset
OL,16,FCouncil says it will try to ease the
OL,17,Fimpact of more than #800,000 worth of
OL,18,Fcuts to "community support contracts"
OL,19,Fby spreading them over two years
OL,20,Frather than one.
