OL,4,Ccuts will put vulnerable people at risk
OL,6,FYouth Connect South West, based in
OL,7,FBath, receives #500,000 a year from
OL,8,FBANES Council but says it is yet to
OL,9,Fdiscover what future funding it will
OL,10,Freceive despite the council already
OL,11,Fsetting its budget.
OL,13,FCEO Tracey Pike said: "We offer a
OL,14,Freally invaluable service to young
OL,15,Fpeople through our early help
OL,16,Fprovision and it's frightening to
OL,17,Fthink there's going to be less
OL,18,Favailable when already demand is over
OL,19,Fsubscribed.
