OL,6,F"If we get less, we'll be working with
OL,7,Ffewer young people and offering fewer
OL,8,Fservices in fewer areas so it will be
OL,9,Freally challenging for everybody."
OL,11,FThe concerns are shared by Julian
OL,12,FHouse which looks after hundreds of
OL,13,Fhomeless people every year, either
OL,14,Fthrough their emergency accommodation
OL,15,Fhostel or temporary accommodation in
OL,16,Fthe community as well as with outreach
OL,17,Fworkers on the streets.
