OL,3,CCharities fear 'shortsighted' funding
OL,4,Ccuts will put vulnerable people at risk
OL,6,FChief Executive Helen Bedser said the
OL,7,Fcharity has suffered a funding gap of
OL,8,F#150,000 for each of the last five
OL,9,Fyears and argues more money is needed
OL,10,Fas demand rises.J"Obviously the
OL,11,Fcouncil is in a really difficult
OL,12,Fposition trying to balance its books,
OL,13,Fbut this feels quite shortsighted
OL,14,Fbecause it will result in increasing
OL,15,Fhomelessness, increasing rough
OL,16,Fsleeping which will have a knock-on
OL,17,Fimpact on adult social care, housing
OL,18,Fand the human impact. It will put
OL,19,Flives at risk," she said.
