OL,6,FMichael Dixon has used the Julian
OL,7,FHouse hostel for four months and says
OL,8,Fit saves lives.
OL,10,F"I think there would be a lot more
OL,11,Ffatalities on the streets with
OL,12,Fhomeless people if this place wasn't
OL,13,Fhere.
OL,15,F"When they talk about cuts to budgets
OL,16,Fit's a big worry, not knowing who it's
OL,17,Fgoing to affect, but ultimately the
OL,18,Fpeople who end up paying are
OL,19,Fvulnerable people," he said.
