OL,6,FThe council is seeking to plug a #24.5
OL,7,Fmillion funding gap and says it will
OL,8,Ftake a "full review with our third
OL,9,Fsector partners, of all community
OL,10,Fcontracts".
OL,12,FCouncillor Mark Elliott, cabinet
OL,13,Fmember for Resources added: "Until
OL,14,Fthat review is undertaken we don't
OL,15,Fwant to dictate specific savings to
OL,16,Fspecific organisations. We spend more
OL,17,Fthan #9m on more than 40 contracts in
OL,18,Fthe third sector.
